                            <comment id="14264661" author="chris@christopherschultz.net" created="Mon, 5 Jan 2015 15:14:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I checked this against the 1.4.1 candidate build and it seems to be working correctly. I then checked against 1.4.0 since very few significant changes have been made to the email validator in a looong time, and the 1.4.0 seems to work as expected. I&apos;m interested in the earliest release in which this has been fixed, so I&apos;ll do a bit of archeology.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
